thread.title: Jolanta Jablonska
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Jolanta Jablonska

author: Jolanta Jablonska
title: Jolanta Jablonska
text: Ink Station are extremely efficient when it comes to delivery of their products. However, once I ordered my printer's ink and the cartridges would not click into the printer, I reported the fault to service department. I was told i was sent the correct items and inks should fit. I have cartridges full of ink lying around somewhere. Apart from this once off issue I would recommend Ink Station to everyone.
